{"tid":1496280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[Tor]匿名論壇介紹","createTime":"2019-08-22T12:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T08:35:16.000Z","uid":244509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"134aa9df2eb2746d084193355daf9190b0e7cf97","tid":1496280,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"大家如果有需要匿名可以用Galaxy3, 之前個8chan香港台唔知做咩收咗皮<br />\n<a href=\"http://galaxy3m2mn5iqtn.onion/groups/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgalaxy3m2mn5iqtn.onion%2Fgroups%2Fall&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=2baf439d\" target=\"_blank\">galaxy3m2mn5iqtn.onion/groups/all</a><br />\n<br />\nGalaxy3 介紹:<br />\n- 註冊後可以開group, 分為open同closed group(只有member先睇到group既內容)<br />\n- closed group需要向group owner request membership, 可以用黎篩走d鬼同3毛<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy3 註冊<br />\n- 註冊email可以亂填, display name同 user name set唔同名, 避免被人撞password登入<br />\n<br />\n開closed group篩人可參考以下steps:<br />\n1. 搵一個有公信力既連登user開group<br />\n2. 大家去個group request membership<br />\n3. group owner留個email, 大家send自己連登同galaxy3既名俾佢<br />\n4. group owner起底後確認user非鬼/3毛, reply email要求在指定連登post留下指定句子(可用不推post回覆), 用黎確認個連登account真係佢<br />\n5. 想入group者到指定post留言後, reply番個email, 提及留言樓層, 方便group owner查核<br />\n6. group owner確認後去group度批準membership<br />\np.s. group owner email請選擇有提供end to end encryption(e.g. protonmail), 保障番大家<br />\np.s. e個做法只有group owner知道大家係同時係連登同galaxy3既身份<br />\n<br />\n進一步隱藏言論, 避免galaxy3 site owner審查<br />\n- 加密內容先post, 加密解密key由group owner係email send俾member"},{"pid":"32798aed090fa508ceeeddf946b58ea5a73dc0b7","tid":1496280,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d31279336245c9a0eea67c92a63b231144d00b","tid":1496280,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n